h2.My journey.h2l

I am transitioning into full-stack development through structured, self-driven learning, with a strong focus on real-world projects. Coming from a non-computer science background, I have developed practical skills in frontend and backend technologies and continue to strengthen my programming fundamentals.

Before this transition, I spent over seven years in customer-facing and technical support roles for global organizations, strengthening my problem-solving, troubleshooting, and communication skills.